video_title: The STORY of who you THINK you are
transcript:
who you think you are what you think
about the world these are stories that
you tell yourself they are not who you
are because it is not possible for any
story to contain the story maker they
exist on two different ontological
planes and any story that you tell
yourself can be retold by that same self
this is the creative potential of the
Free Will which may be the spark of the
Divine that exists within all of us
